flowchart TD
    START([New Project]) --> BOOT[bootstrap-corezero.sh<br/>copy skills + memory + rules]
    BOOT --> DETECT{Detect repo state}

    DETECT -->|empty / near-empty| GREEN[Greenfield Mode]
    DETECT -->|existing code + tests + history| BROWN[Brownfield Mode]

    GREEN --> GINIT[starter-init<br/>Auto-fill harness-config<br/>+ Tier 1 templates from code]
    GINIT --> GMEM[context-memory<br/>Seed constitution / security<br/>/ project-knowledge-base]
    GMEM --> GFEAT[Pick first feature]

    BROWN --> BARCH[brownfield-init<br/>map debt + dependencies<br/>+ risky paths]
    BARCH --> BINIT[starter-init<br/>bootstrap harness after archaeology]
    BINIT --> BREAD[Read brownfield map<br/>before first feature]
    BREAD --> BSAFE[Pick smallest safe<br/>first feature]

    GFEAT --> LOOP[Guided per-feature loop]
    BSAFE --> LOOP
    LOOP --> SHIP([Ship + Self-Improving KB])

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef green fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    classDef brown fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef common fill:#fff,stroke:#d0d7de,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef decision fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#0d0d0d

    class START,SHIP terminal
    class GREEN,GINIT,GMEM,GFEAT green
    class BROWN,BARCH,BINIT,BREAD,BSAFE brown
    class BOOT,LOOP common
    class DETECT decision
